N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2100.17 - Substitution of applicable dates

State Regulations

Parts 2100 to 2109, inclusive, of this Subchapter are
applicable to housing accommodations within the city of Albany; provided, however, that wherever March 1, 1950 appears therein, April 1, 1962 shall be
substituted, and wherever May 1, 1950 appears therein, June 30, 1963 shall be
substituted. Notes
